                <div class="tab-content">
                    <div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-script">
                        <div class="js-script-content-wrapper top-margin-script markdown-content">
                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/rest/edit/master/knpu/episode2/reuse-consistency.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>Now I want to do a couple of other cleanup things. First: whenever we need to
read information off of the request that the client is sending us, we're going 
to use this same <code>json_decode</code> for the content:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="b4f7a37cdd">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
            <span class="fa fa-clipboard js-activate-clipboard" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Copy Code" data-placement="top"></span>
        </div>
