<h2 id="a-parameterbag-makes-life-nicer">A ParameterBag Makes Life Nicer <a class="headerlink" href="reuse-consistency#a-parameterbag-makes-life-nicer" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>One last little thing that is going to make our code even easier to deal with.
Back in <code>TokenController</code>, because the <code>decodeRequestBodyIntoParameters</code>
returns an array, we need to code a bit more defensively here. What if they 
don't actually send a <code>notes</code> key, we don't want some sort of PHP error:</p>
