<h2 id="use-decoderequestbodyintoparameters-in-all-the-places">Use decodeRequestBodyIntoParameters in all the Places <a class="headerlink" href="reuse-consistency#use-decoderequestbodyintoparameters-in-all-the-places" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>We have this really nice new function inside of our <code>BaseController</code> and 
I also want to take advantage of it inside of our <code>ProgrammerController</code>.
We're going down to <code>handleRequest</code> and now we can just say 
<code>$data = $this-&gt;decodeRequestBodyIntoParameters()</code> and pass the <code>$request</code>
