<p>Lovely! Now that was a fairly fundamental change so there is a good chance that we
broke something. So let's go back and run our entire programmer feature:</p>
<pre><code>php vendor/bin/behat features/api/programmer.feature</code></pre>
<p>Beautiful! We didn't actually break anything which is so good to know.</p>

    
